{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_11_level_main_11-05_beg","storyGroup":"main_11","storySort":98,"storyDependence":"main_11_level_main_11-05_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"11-6","storyName":"演绎文明","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"莱托试图说服掌握着自救军情报的戈尔丁投向城防军。变形者接近戈尔丁，Logos追着变形者而来，与变形者借戏对谈。\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_11-05_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_11-05","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":8,"next":10,"characters":["戈尔丁","莱托中校","茉莉","？？？","变形者集群","“茉莉”","“神秘观众”"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_bg_32_g3_school_indoor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.7","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"你来这里做什么？","id":12,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"就像我说的那样，只是来看一场演出。","id":14,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#3$1","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"......孩子们，都到我身后来。","id":16,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":17},{"type":"character","id":18},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crowdrun","volume":"1","id":19},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":20},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"莱托中校，无意冒犯，但这里不欢迎你。","id":22,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#10$1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"我们不用这么生分吧，戈尔丁。","id":24,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"我一向认同你的努力，越是艰难的时代，教育的重要性就越应该被凸显出来。","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"中校先生，您这么说，好像自己和这个“艰难的时代”没什么关系似的。","id":28,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"不管什么时代，您穿得可总是十足体面。","id":30,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"您胸前的勋章也越来越多了。","id":32,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#8$1","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"协助军事委员会管理伦蒂尼姆不是一件轻松的事情，我也遇到了很多......困难。","id":34,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"但我对这座城市的热爱始终未曾改变，就这点而言，我和你们一样。","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"鞋匠汤姆肯定很赞同。","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#6$1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"汤姆也是我的朋友，发生那样的事我并不乐意见到。","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/99/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"他只是喝醉了酒，嘟囔“陛下”和“蒸汽骑士”什么的，他甚至不怎么会拼“萨卡兹”。","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"他还活着。","id":44,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我们存在的意义不只是活着。","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#7$1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"你想指控我为维多利亚的叛徒吗，戈尔丁？","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"——","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#5$1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"女士们，我敬佩你们的勇气。","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/98/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#2$1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"不过你们误会了。","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/98/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"我今天来这里，只是想再看一看这所学校罢了。","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"茉莉小姐，很遗憾，看来你已经忘记我了。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"......忘记？","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"我在这里度过的时间不比你少，茉莉小姐。我甚至还记得你和同你一起来的那批孩子。","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"很遗憾，军校毕业后，我的空闲时间就没有那么多了。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#10$1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"可戈尔丁，你曾是信任我的。我们时常一起谈论高卢的历史，聊起那些不朽的文学——","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"够了，莱托中校。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我十分感谢你的父亲，他多年来一直资助着这所学校，他试图为孩子们点燃智慧的火炬，驱散蒙昧与混沌。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我曾以为你是和他一样的人......而你，却亲手熄灭了那点本就微弱的火光。","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"是吗？戈尔丁，那你觉得，这所学校为什么能维持到今天？","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"你——你别想威胁我们！","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#8$1","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"我并没有威胁各位的理由和动机，孩子们还在呢。","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"戈尔丁女士，我们都是高卢遗民。","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"我们都知道，战争是最无情的毁灭者，除了带走成千上万的生命，还会摧毁人类为通向智识做出的一切努力。","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"我不想看见伦蒂尼姆变成下一个林贡斯，也不想让刚才看到的如此美好的戏剧演出就此绝迹。","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#8$1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"这是我为我自己选择的责任。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......我无法赞同你的看法。","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"林贡斯的皇家歌剧院已经化作灰烬，而《凯旋颂》仍在各时各地被反复演绎。","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"建筑会倒塌，巨构会瓦解，但我们曾凝集其中的结晶却永不会消亡。那是我们的教育、我们的文化、我们的希望。","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"战争的阴云越是浓烈，我们就越是需要坚持信念，需要相信美的东西，来提醒自己身为人类与野兽的差别。","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"你相信这种对抗能赢？","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"你们所代表的那些东西，恐惧、权力、杀戮......永远无法驯化每一个人。","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我必须相信。","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......我只能相信。","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"只要有光，我们就会向光而行。","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"那我羡慕你，戈尔丁女士。","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"看看头顶的阴云吧，暴风雨就快来了。","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"在落雷之前，我们都还有时间，我们都还有选择。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"希望有一天......我能看到这出戏的结尾。","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":112},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":115},{"type":"character","id":116},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e5/Avg_bg_32_g1_lentiavenue.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":117},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":118},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":119,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":120},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":121},{"type":"text","text":"离开学校之后，城防军指挥官并未在街上停留。","id":122},{"type":"text","text":"他的确是一个人来的，并没有更多城防军官兵来到附近。","id":123},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"她必须找到亚当斯，将消息传出去。","id":126},{"type":"text","text":"不管那位指挥官表现得多么没有敌意，他都不会无缘无故地找上他们学校。","id":127},{"type":"text","text":"茉莉不知道，孩子们不知道，可是戈尔丁知道他为什么会来。","id":128},{"type":"dialog","id":129},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","volume":"1","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"0.5","id":131},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":132},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":133},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":134},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"0.5","id":135},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":136},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","id":137},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":138},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#4$1","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"怎么突然这么多萨卡兹？","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7d/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"通往书店的路很熟悉，她在过去两年多的时间里走了无数回。","id":141},{"type":"text","text":"可今天这条路突然变得很长，长到一眼望不到头，她又想到了萨卡兹进城的那一天。","id":142},{"type":"text","text":"她真的能够改变吗？","id":143},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#6$1","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我必须相信，我必须......","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"戈尔丁突然感觉到自己被一种恐惧扼住了咽喉。","id":146},{"type":"text","text":"她简直要吐出来了，她转身逃离。","id":147},{"type":"dialog","id":148},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":149},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":150},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":151},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":152},{"type":"dialog","id":153},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":154},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"character","id":156},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":157},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_bg_21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":158},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":160},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":161},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"兰西，帕蒂！","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#8$1","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"这些孩子......！兰——","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.7","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"——","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_npc_426_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":168},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":169},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"40","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":170},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_punch02","volume":"1","id":171},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":172},{"type":"dialog","id":173},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":174},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#4$1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"唔——！","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown2","volume":"1","id":178},{"type":"move","name":"middle","ypos":"-20","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":180},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":181},{"type":"dialog","id":182},{"type":"character","id":183},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":184},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":185},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"......或许这样简单的任务并不值得劳您大驾，阁下。","id":187,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"那样的话，你应该选择把戈尔丁女士抓起来，莱托。","id":189,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_npc_426_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"曼弗雷德就会这么做。换作老红眼病的话，整座学校都不会剩下一个活口。","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_npc_426_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#4$1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"......","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"好啦，我们知道你不是萨卡兹。你还想着给自己，给城防军，给这座城市里的居民留一点最后的体面。","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/26/Avg_avg_npc_426_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":196},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":197},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"但我们相信这样会更保险。","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#4$1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"您......","id":201,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#8$1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"兰西，帕蒂......不知道孩子们有没有危险。","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"中校先生，我很害怕。我既害怕像您这样的人和萨卡兹伤害孩子们，也害怕......孩子们变成像您一样的人。","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#4$1","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"......您的语气和这位昏迷的女士一模一样。","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"嗯......我们在感受。","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"她关心那些年幼的维多利亚人，胜过关心自己。我们能感受到，却很难理解。尤其这种关心还不是基于血缘。","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"......","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"......阁下？","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"我们对你们很感兴趣。透过你们，我们能更好地理解自己......理解萨卡兹。","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"您想从我们身上找寻一些答案？关于......什么的答案？","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"莱托，你并不像那种对萨卡兹感到好奇的人。","id":221,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#5$1","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"抱歉，阁下。","id":223,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/98/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"任务是第一优先的。","id":225,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"把这位茉莉小姐带回去吧，中校先生。看好她。我们会留在戈尔丁女士身边，为接下来的战争取得更多情报。","id":227,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"是，阁下。","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#5$1","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"......","id":231,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/22/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#1$1","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"怎么了，阁下？","id":233,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"有人发现我们了。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_649_1#7$1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱托中校","text":"是否需要我让更多士兵过来？","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_649_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"不必了，士兵们拦不住他。","id":239,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"他从特蕾西娅那里学到了不少。我们也许很快就能......轻松地聊聊天。","id":241,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":242},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":243},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":245},{"type":"character","id":246},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_bg_32_g3_school_indoor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":247},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":248},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":249,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":250},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":251},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.7","id":252},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":253},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"......","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......茉莉。","id":257,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"嗯？","id":259,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"在我出去的这段时间，没出什么事吧？","id":261,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"没有，兰西和帕蒂吓坏了，拉尔夫那几个大孩子带着小家伙们休息去了。","id":263,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"那就好。我在想......孩子们会喜欢这些戏的吧？","id":265,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我们的努力是有意义的，对吧？","id":267,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"您在说什么？","id":269,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/29/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"不......没什么。","id":271,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/48/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"您不用在意那个城防军指挥官的话，戈尔丁女士。","id":273,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我，我不是很舒服，我想休息一下。","id":275,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"抱歉，茉莉，这里就麻烦你收拾了。","id":277,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d1/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"没事的。","id":279,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"这出戏该有一个结尾的，蒸汽骑士已经走到王宫门前了。","id":281,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"过几天，孩子们会把最后一幕演完的，对吗？","id":283,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_647_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......一定。","id":285,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_647_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":286},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":287},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-300","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":288},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":289},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":290},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"一个故事的结尾只要没被演绎，就总是有很多种可能性的。","id":292,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#6$1","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"可是，已经上演的戏，也未必无法改变，人们总是想看到更新鲜的版本。","id":294,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":295},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#7$1","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"......你在一旁看了很久了，是吧？","id":297,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":298},{"type":"character","id":299},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":300},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_650_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.7","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":302,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_650_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"既然舞台还在，我们能不能重新演一遍呢？从第一幕开始。","id":304,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_650_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.7","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"所有人都总是在幻想，如果一切没有发生会怎样。","id":306,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_650_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_650_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.7","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"推演没有意义。","id":308,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7e/Avg_avg_npc_650_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#7$1","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"但如果只是些渺茫的可能性......","id":310,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_657_1#1$1","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"茉莉","text":"好先生，若您正好闲来无事，不如加入这场演出吧？","id":312,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9a/Avg_avg_npc_657_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":313},{"type":"character","id":314},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":315},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":316},{"type":"background","id":317},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":318},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":319,"musicid":3},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_32_i02.png","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","x":"0","y":"150","fadetime":"1","id":320},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"早安，阁下！您的脸上布满愁容，请问是什么让您如此心焦？","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"胜利的号角声已在城墙上盘旋了三天三夜，可我的心为何还是如此焦灼？","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"我们伟大的将军不是早已凯旋了吗？赞美他的英勇与无畏！","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"英勇？无畏？也许是的。","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"一次激进的号召，将我们的信念凝成一团。代价，却是近在眼前的毁灭和仇恨。","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"你本该侍奉一位君主，却将你的忠诚献给了一位贼人。","id":327},{"type":"dialog","id":328},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":329},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":330},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_32_i02.png","xScale":"1.5","yScale":"1.5","x":"-290","y":"100","id":331},{"type":"imagetween","image":"32_i02","fadetime":"0.5","xScaleFrom":"1.5","yScaleFrom":"1.5","xScaleTo":"1.5","yScaleTo":"1.5","xfrom":"-290","yfrom":"100","xTo":"-290","yTo":"80","duration":"10","id":332},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","channel":"n","loop":"false","id":334},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"n","fadetime":"1","id":335},{"type":"text","text":"舞台上，神秘的观众向前一步，视线从眼前人的身上移向了远方。","id":336},{"type":"text","text":"他并非在酝酿情绪，相反，他在整理那些早已尘封的关于另一处战场的往事。","id":337},{"type":"dialog","id":338},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":339},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":340},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_32_i02.png","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","x":"0","y":"150","id":341},{"type":"imagetween","image":"32_i02","fadetime":"0.5","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1.15","yScaleTo":"1.15","xfrom":"0","yfrom":"150","xTo":"0","yTo":"150","duration":"10","id":342},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"我追随的并非君主，而是一种正直，一股勇气。","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"再往前走的话，迎接你的只有毁灭。","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"活着看到这个国家被暴君带着走向毁灭，远比个体毁灭更可怕。","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"你怎知她的结局，阁下？","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"我能预见她的结局，正如我知晓她的来路。","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"胡说！你尚年幼，怎敢张口怀念往昔？","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"谁能令太阳永不下落？生出这种欲望本就是最大的贪婪。","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"为了维系这盛大的光辉，我见过无数疯狂之举。他们或是化身强盗，或是相互争斗，最终只会加速这个国家的腐朽。","id":351},{"type":"dialog","id":352},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":353},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":354},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_32_i02.png","xScale":"1.5","yScale":"1.5","x":"290","y":"80","id":355},{"type":"imagetween","image":"32_i02","fadetime":"0.5","xScaleFrom":"1.5","yScaleFrom":"1.5","xScaleTo":"1.5","yScaleTo":"1.5","xfrom":"290","yfrom":"80","xTo":"250","yTo":"80","duration":"10","id":356},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":357},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","channel":"n","loop":"false","id":358},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"n","fadetime":"1","id":359},{"type":"dialog","id":360},{"type":"character","id":361},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":362},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.3","id":363},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","channel":"n","loop":"false","id":364},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"n","fadetime":"1","id":365},{"type":"text","text":"“茉莉”在舞台上转了个身，轻踱几步，再回过身，将面目隐藏在灯光下的阴影里。","id":366},{"type":"text","text":"但另一位演员先开口了，他神色沉静如水，微微侧手，又将双手交叉。","id":367},{"type":"dialog","id":368},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":369},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":370},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_32_i02.png","xScale":"1.15","yScale":"1.15","x":"0","y":"150","fadetime":"1","id":371},{"type":"imagetween","image":"32_i02","fadetime":"0.5","xScaleFrom":"1.15","yScaleFrom":"1.15","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","xfrom":"0","yfrom":"150","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","duration":"15","id":372},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"他们不愿承认，下坠之人想要攀住日光，握在手中的却只可能是闪电。","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"难道人们就只能甘愿坠落？","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"人们也可以选择不再回望山巅。","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"假使他们掉转自己的视线，他们会发现面前的深渊不是深渊，而是包含无穷可能性的沃土。","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“茉莉”","text":"深渊可被战胜？你并不清楚深渊的真相，也未必知晓，时间紧迫。","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“神秘观众”","text":"深渊就在身前，我等可用肉身填于深渊，用鲜血烧尽残垣，给后人留下一片广阔原野。","id":379},{"type":"dialog","id":380},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":381},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.9","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":382},{"type":"subtitle","text":"只有等到旧日的灰烬全部被吹散，原野上才能长出新的粮食，来喂饱我们的下一代。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":383},{"type":"subtitle","id":384},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":385},{"type":"dialog","id":386},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":387},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":388},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":389},{"type":"character","id":390},{"type":"image","id":391}],"characters":["戈尔丁","莱托中校","茉莉","？？？","变形者集群","“茉莉”","“神秘观众”"]}